Food composition data
======================

The nutrient values embedded in catalog.json (energy and macronutrients per 100 g)
are derived from:

    USDA FoodData Central, SR Legacy, release 2018-04
    https://fdc.nal.usda.gov/
    License: CC0 1.0 Universal (Public Domain Dedication)
    https://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/

USDA FDC data is released into the public domain (CC0): it may be embedded and
redistributed freely, with attribution requested but not required.

Hand-authored additions:
  - Italian names (name_it) and synonyms are authored locally. Food NAMES are not
    a licensed asset; the composition NUMBERS are, and those come from CC0 FDC.
  - A few Italian staples absent from SR Legacy (bresaola, prosciutto crudo,
    Grana Padano) and sports-nutrition products (energy gels, bars, maltodextrin,
    isotonic drinks) are hand-entered from manufacturer nutrition labels. Label
    figures are facts, not a copyrightable asset. Each such row carries source +
    as_of and is refreshable: branded formulations change over time.

This catalog is for general, personal, non-clinical use. It is not a substitute
for a dietitian or, for children, a pediatrician.
